results.name: Number of centered 5-valent trees with n nodes.
link: E. M. Rains and N. J. A. Sloane, On Cayley's Enumeration of Alkanes (or 4-Valent Trees), J. Integer Sequences, Vol. 2 (1999), Article 99.1.1.
Index entries for sequences related to trees
mathematica: n = 30; (* algorithm from Rains and Sloane *)
T[-1,z_] := 1;  T[h_,z_] := T[h,z] = Table[z^k, {k,0,n}].Take[CoefficientList[z^(n+1) + 1 + S4[T,h-1,z]z, z], n+1];
Sum[Take[CoefficientList[z^(n+1) + S5[T,h-1,z]z - S5[T,h-2,z]z - (T[h-1,z] - T[h-2,z]) (T[h-1,z]-1),z], n+1], {h,1,n/2}] + PadRight[{0,1}, n+1] (* _Robert A. Russell_, Sep 15 2018 *)
